video.title: Roswell, New Mexico
video.synopsis: After 10 years, a woman returns to her sleepy hometown and discovers her high-school crush is also an unusual foreigner.

episodes.synopsis: A decade after the death of her sister, Liz reluctantly returns to her small hometown and reconnects with her teenage crush Max.
episodes.title: Pilot

episodes.synopsis: On the anniversary of her sister’s death, Liz searches for answers. Meanwhile, Max defends his relationship with Liz against his siblings' criticism.
episodes.title: So Much For the Afterglow

episodes.synopsis: Suspicious of Max’s involvement in Rosa’s death, Liz taps Maria to find out more about her sister’s last days.
episodes.title: Tearin' Up My Heart

episodes.synopsis: When a local hospital goes dark, Max grapples with using his powers to help. Liz confronts Kyle to learn more about who killed Rosa.
episodes.title: Where Have All the Cowboys Gone

episodes.synopsis: Liz gets caught in a dangerous crossfire when shes coaxes a local documentarian. Isobel suffers a series of mysterious blackouts.
episodes.title: Don't Speak

episodes.synopsis: Flashbacks to 2008 uncover a bevy of secrets about Rosa’s last day, the truth about Isobel’s blackouts and the start of Alex and Michael’s relationship.
episodes.title: Smells Like Teen Spirit

episodes.synopsis: After spending a day with Mimi, Maria, and Alex, Liz has a devastating revelation. Later, Max asks Liz to help him lead a normal life.
episodes.title: I Saw the Sign

episodes.synopsis: As Isobel's health deteriorates, Liz and Michael search for ways to help. Max turns to his mother for answers about his alien symbol.
episodes.title: Barely Breathing

episodes.synopsis: In search of a cure for Isobel and Maria's sick mother, Max, Michael, Liz and Maria travel to Texas to meet a faith healer.
episodes.title: Songs About Texas

episodes.synopsis: Liz helps Isobel regain her memories, which provides an alternative conclusion about Rosa's demise. A mysterious murder streak draws attention.
episodes.title: I Don't Want to Miss a Thing

episodes.synopsis: While the UFO Emporium Grand Reopening Gala distracts Roswell, Liz, Michael and Isobel face off with an unsuspecting threat.
episodes.title: Champagne Supernova

episodes.synopsis: While Max, Michael, and Isobel disagree on how to handle a tough situation, Alex, Kyle and Michael uncover more secrets about Project Shepherd.
episodes.title: Creep

episodes.synopsis: As a new presence draws a wedge between Max and Michael, Kyle unearths a shocking secret. Liz reunites with an unexpected visitor.
episodes.title: Recovering the Satellites

episodes.synopsis: Suppressing her emotions, Liz sets her sights on leaving town as Rosa experiences strange side effects during her recovery.
episodes.title: Stay (I Missed You)

episodes.synopsis: Rosa confronts Liz over her reputation. Michael helps Maria with a family matter. Isobel faces a major personal decision.
episodes.title: Ladies and Gentlemen We Are Floating in Space

episodes.synopsis: An uneasy duo, Michael and Alex team up for an investigation as Isobel wrestles with inner turmoil. Elsewhere, Maria seeks answers from Liz.
episodes.title: Good Mother

episodes.synopsis: When Liz tries to make a breakthrough with Kyle's help, Michael and Alex get clarity on the past. Isobel uses her skills to change someone's mind.
episodes.title: What If God Was One Of Us?

episodes.synopsis: Liz and Michael consider the possibilities concerning Max while Isobel works to confirm Rosa's claims. Then, Maria digs deeper into her family.
episodes.title: I'll Stand By You

episodes.synopsis: As Liz deals with a stunning setback, Maria takes Alex on a mission that rocks their lives. Isobel's outing leads to unexpected encounters.
episodes.title: Sex and Candy

episodes.synopsis: An unwanted family reunion raises suspicion for both Liz and Rosa. Meanwhile, Maria has a strange vision about Kyle that draws Michael's concern.
episodes.title: Como La Flor

episodes.synopsis: Despite having a new persona, Rosa's old ways guide her future. Maria tests a new talent while a missing person search yields shocking results.
episodes.title: Say It Ain't So

episodes.synopsis: Michael, Isobel and Alex learn the stark truth about their families through an unlikely source as the town sheriff's investigation points elsewhere.
episodes.title: The Diner

episodes.synopsis: Full of questions, Alex takes a group on the road and finds much more than answers. Back at home, a crisis erupts between Liz and her father.
episodes.title: American Woman

episodes.synopsis: Liz considers sharing her latest findings with a past flame. Michael searches for Alex's whereabouts while Kyle gets enlisted for an investigation.
episodes.title: Linger

episodes.synopsis: Friends, family and foes collide at the town's biggest event of the year when a deadly plot puts everyone's lives in jeopardy.
episodes.title: Crash Into Me

episodes.synopsis: As a threat hits their town, the group finally unlocks the truth about Roswell's past. Later, Liz receives a life-changing offer.
episodes.title: Mr. Jones
Killing Me Softly With His Song
I Ain't Goin' Out Like That
